pageContext.claim: “Matthew G. Whitaker is a highly respected former U.S. Attorney from Iowa. He was chosen by Jeff Sessions to be his Chief of Staff. I did not know Mr. Whitaker. Likewise, as Chief, I did not know Mr. Whitaker except primarily as he traveled with A.G. Sessions. No social contact.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump may not know Matt Whitaker well, but he had met with him several time in the Oval Office and has previously claimed to "know Matt Whitaker."
